metadata.name: The Marks Of Age
metadata.description:
Twisted exposed wood from a dead tree showing bizarre shapes and textures mimics the marks of age on our own skin.  
This triptych is made up of three high quality photographs and is available as a 1 of 1 as a celebration of the end of 2022 and the start of 2023.

Artist: Paul Moon  
Location: East Yorkshire, United Kingdom.  
Image size: 14650px x 6855px
